- `upload-feature/` - groups all upload-related components
- `creator-badge/` - groups all creator badge components
- `tools-feature/` - groups all tool-related components
- `dropdown-controls/` - groups all dropdown components

### ⚠️ Review Needed
- `base-panel/` - if only one component, consider moving to root
- `result-image-preview/` - good feature grouping
- `landing-page/` - good feature grouping

## Index Files

### Pattern for index.ts
```typescript
// ✅ CORRECT - named exports only
export { ComponentName } from "./component-name";
export * from "./component-name";

// ❌ WRONG - default export
export default ComponentName;
```

### When to Use Index Files
- Use when folder contains multiple related components
- Use to provide cleaner import paths
- Optional for single-component folders
